<Entity class="oracle.dbtools.crest.model.design.logical.Entity" directorySegmentName="seg_3" id="F113ACC3-8DA5-8E54-6DD7-91545BD2BAF3" name="Tranche in a Traditional securitisation">
<createdBy>Dominik</createdBy>
<createdTime>2021-08-11 13:29:56 UTC</createdTime>
<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[Regulation (EU) 2402/2017, Article 2, (6):
´Tranche’ means a contractually established segment of the credit risk associated with an exposure or a pool of exposures, where a position in the segment entails a risk of credit loss greater than or less than a position of the same amount in another segment, without taking account of credit protection provided by third parties directly to the holders of positions in the segment or in other segments.]]></commentInRDBMS>
